snippet.title: The Local - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The Local is a fast-paced parkour delivery game set in the Australian outback. Rail grind around the long abandoned country to complete orders. Master the movement mechanics, avoid obstacles, and go for the highscore!

WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM!
